'''''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 140''' is the one hundred fortieth issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[November]] [[1980]].

The series, previously titled ''The Empire Strikes Back Weekly'', was renamed when it switched to a monthly publishing schedule. This was also the first issue to reprint an entire US comic book story in a single issue.

